betterquesting:10.desc:8:
Next we need some wiring for that fancy new Circuit Plate you just crafted.  All you need is some copper.  There are several ways to make the circuit wiring.  You can craft it by hand with 8 Fine Copper Wires and your wire cutters or you can use a Precision Laser Engraver and Copper Foil.  Doing it by hand will use more copper.
§b
Note:  You will need to have T1 Basic Circuits to make a Laser Engraver(T1)
§6
Completely by hand: Anvil Plate into 2 Foils -> Cut Foil into 1 Fine Copper Wire => Requires 4 Copper plates for 8 fine Copper Wire
Use Cluster Mill:  1 Copper Plate into 4 Foils -> Use Cutters to make Fine Copper Wire => 2 Copper plates for 8 Fine Copper Wire
Use Wire Mill:  1 Copper Rod wil make 4 Fine Copper Wires => 1 Copper Ingot (2 Copper Rods) for 8 Fine Copper Wire
Use Cluster Mill/Laser Engraver:  1 Copper Plate in Cluster Mill for 4 Copper Foil, 4 Copper Foil in Laser Engraver will create 1 Circuit Wiring.
§a
To Complete the quest craft:
1 Circuit Wiring (Copper)
